1
00:00:12,100 --> 00:00:13,260
Did you bring it?

2
00:00:16,740 --> 00:00:18,540
So this is
the Shadow Clan's divine artifact,

3
00:00:19,060 --> 00:00:20,140
the Fushi Mirror?

4
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:21,660
With it,

5
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:23,980
I can cultivate the ancient forbidden art

6
00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:26,380
to enhance my power.

7
00:00:26,860 --> 00:00:27,540
Correct.

8
00:00:30,460 --> 00:00:31,940
I will assist you with the ritual.

9
00:00:32,260 --> 00:00:33,700
Focus on your cultivation.

10
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:35,380
Alright.

11
00:01:05,940 --> 00:01:06,500
You...

12
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:14,080
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 23]

13
00:01:29,740 --> 00:01:30,540
Wan'er.

14
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:32,980
Your illness has flared up again.

15
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:36,940
I'm fine.

16
00:01:37,940 --> 00:01:39,260
Don't waste your power on saving me.

17
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:07,660
- Wan'er, are you alright?
- It's her!

18
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:09,420
It's her! I've seen her before.

19
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:10,860
She's the one who killed you.

20
00:02:10,980 --> 00:02:11,420
It's her...

21
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,340
Yang.

22
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:27,500
Master.

23
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:29,500
You're finally back.

24
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:33,260
I finally did it.

25
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:37,700
I'm Ruoxi.

26
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:38,860
Yang.

27
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,660
I don't want to

28
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:41,900
be your master.

29
00:02:46,220 --> 00:02:46,780
Yang.

30
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:47,860
Wake up.

31
00:03:06,540 --> 00:03:07,340
Xiyin.

32
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:09,060
It's you.

33
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:10,700
What are you doing here?

34
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:14,740
You all need to leave now.

35
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:24,100
Immortal Venerable.

36
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:37,780
The Immortal Venerable
has already got the Fushi Mirror back.

37
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:39,100
What did you say?

38
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:40,700
She already knows

39
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:41,500
where you're hiding.

40
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,460
You've been exposed.

41
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:43,980
Run now before it's too late.

42
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:46,340
Not good.

43
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:48,740
Trying to trap me? Not a chance.

44
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:08,220
Take Yaoyang with you!

45
00:04:23,940 --> 00:04:24,860
Go now!

46
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:26,900
I'll remember

47
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:27,980
this favor.

48
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:31,460
Heng,

49
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:33,100
you really let me down.

50
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:46,740
We should split up.

51
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:47,780
No.

52
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:49,660
I'm their target.

53
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,580
You take care of Yaoyang.

54
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:57,220
Xiyin.

55
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:02,380
You can't escape.

56
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,060
We'll see about that.

57
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:22,740
Another one here to die.

58
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:24,700
We'll see

59
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:25,820
who ends up dead!

60
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:27,740
What are you doing here?

61
00:05:27,940 --> 00:05:28,860
Is it that strange?

62
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:31,300
We're on the same side now.

63
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:33,500
Take this demon core.

64
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:34,940
Let's fight our way out together!

65
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,980
I can't die yet.

66
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:38,500
I have to save Yaoyang.

67
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:43,300
She's about to become a fiend.

68
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:49,980
Go now!

69
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:52,740
Capturing Xieyun is the priority!

70
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:03,460
Xiyin.

71
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,340
Give up now.

72
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:06,900
For the greater good.

73
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,780
And for your own sake as well.

74
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:43,500
Ruoxi.

75
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,260
Leave now.

76
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:47,460
Tu Jing.

77
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:26,300
We made it out.

78
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:27,660
Hang in there.

79
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:28,940
I'll save you right away.

80
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:33,860
There's no time.

81
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:35,460
No, there is.

82
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:36,500
- It's too late.
- No.

83
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:37,460
No, it's not.

84
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:42,900
Actually,

85
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:46,060
I knew from the start

86
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,300
that the person you like

87
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:53,100
is Yaoyang.

88
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:56,700
I know it.

89
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:01,740
I also know

90
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:04,860
you've never really changed.

91
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,900
It's all been an act.

92
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:13,420
♪Already steal my sleep?♪

93
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:17,180
♪If the prophecy begins♪

94
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,220
Actually,

95
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:22,940
I met you even before Yaoyang did.

96
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:26,860
The first time I saw you,

97
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,540
you were dressed

98
00:08:29,540 --> 00:08:31,380
♪This life feels like our first sight♪

99
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,460
all in white.

100
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:35,320
♪For you, I drew the Three-Lives Blade♪

101
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:37,300
Who's there?

102
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:42,140
♪Carving eternity before your eyes♪

103
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:44,740
So it's just a little fox.

104
00:08:44,740 --> 00:08:45,820
♪If saying goodbye aloud♪

105
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,300
♪Allows us to meet again♪

106
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:50,100
So

107
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:52,860
it was you
hiding behind the tree that day

108
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:54,900
after collecting

109
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:57,060
the immortal dew.

110
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:09,100
No.

111
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:10,100
Little Fox.

112
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:10,820
Little Fox!

113
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:12,020
Wake up.

114
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:13,060
Wake up.

115
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:14,700
No.

116
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:28,660
♪This life feels like our first sight♪

117
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:29,300
No way.

118
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:30,940
I can't become a fiend.

119
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:34,660
♪For you, I drew the Three-Lives Blade♪

120
00:09:34,780 --> 00:09:40,220
♪Carving eternity before your eyes♪

121
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:40,940
Ruoxi.

122
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:42,420
No.

123
00:09:42,420 --> 00:09:45,380
♪If saying goodbye aloud♪

124
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:49,180
♪Allows us to meet again♪

125
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:56,580
♪Please remember your promise♪

126
00:09:56,840 --> 00:10:08,960
♪Don't forget the vow you made♪

127
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:28,340
What trick are you trying to pull

128
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:29,580
by calling me here?

129
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:31,660
Only you can save my master now.

130
00:10:32,100 --> 00:10:32,940
Your master?

131
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:42,220
My master's soul
has returned to her body.

132
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,580
Use the Fushi Mirror

133
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,580
to draw Xieyun into me,

134
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:47,300
and she'll return to normal.

135
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,380
What a pity.

136
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:50,780
The Immortal Venerable

137
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:53,060
is already prepared to seal Xieyun away.

138
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:54,380
You're too late.

139
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,380
As long as Xieyun is drawn into me,

140
00:10:56,580 --> 00:10:57,700
I'm willing to be sealed away.

141
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:01,980
Why should I believe you?

142
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:03,380
This concerns my master's life.

143
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:04,460
I wouldn't lie to you!

144
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:13,180
I'll trust you this once.

145
00:11:51,020 --> 00:11:53,760
♪What is flickering?♪

146
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:56,500
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

147
00:11:56,660 --> 00:12:02,500
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

148
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:05,380
♪What is falling?♪

149
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:08,620
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

150
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:14,060
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

151
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:16,580
♪When petals drift down♪

152
00:12:16,620 --> 00:12:18,080
♪When the rain falls all around♪

153
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:20,780
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

154
00:12:20,940 --> 00:12:22,640
♪Beyond the dunes♪

155
00:12:22,740 --> 00:12:24,020
♪No end in sight♪

156
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:27,020
♪I am like a mayfly♪

157
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:28,580
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

158
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:30,080
♪Nor will I run away♪

159
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:33,040
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

160
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:38,300
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

161
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:55,360
♪What is flickering?♪

162
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:58,060
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

163
00:12:58,260 --> 00:13:04,060
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

164
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:07,300
♪What is falling?♪

165
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:10,240
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

166
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:15,460
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

167
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:18,060
♪When petals drift down♪

168
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:19,560
♪When the rain falls all around♪

169
00:13:19,660 --> 00:13:22,220
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
